{"tid":2214460,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"想開一個樹窿電台 求各連登巴絲集思廣益","createTime":"2020-09-23T09:18:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-23T09:18:56.000Z","uid":87396,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f92b508b429d4034a8eba3b5ecc2edfc82327934","tid":2214460,"uid":87396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T09:18:56.000Z","msg":"大家好 由於近期腥港實在太唔開心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n加上發覺太多 真。香港人 實在太唔鐘意表達自己內心 成日收收埋埋 鬱住鬱住 遲早出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以想開一個平台 好似電台咁嘅型式比大家一個講出自己嘅心事 感情又好 事業又好 朋友又好 家庭都好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />只要你肯講 我肯聽 <br />\n<br />\n但係依家需要集思廣益一個方法搵一個平台 可以比人phone in到 觀眾又聽到<br />\n<br />\n暫時搞左個ig儲住人先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />ig投稿講都得  如果電台搞得成 將會電台直播時講<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nig： treehole_radio<br />\n<br />\n希望各位高抬貴手 多多支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">黑警死全家 死完爸爸死媽媽</span></span>"}]}